name: Save The UFO
description:
Save The UFO is an arcade game, were you need to save the UFO by playing the role of Aliens.  

An UFO is lossing  it's control, So by playing the role of an aliens you need save the UFO.

• Save The UFO Main Feature =>
• -Saving the UFO with very precise physics.
• -UFO with good graphics hd.
• -Moving the Aliens with Effect add Score when the UFO left the screen.
